#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_posts/2020-05-12-native-command-mode-tools.adoc:74
msgid ""
"Building for Mac just means to provide another job with `runs-on: "
"macos-latest`."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_posts/2020-05-12-native-command-mode-tools.adoc:77
msgid ""
"Windows is essentially the same but requires a little more attention and "
"knowledge about the tooling. Getting it working required some investigation "
"on how the native build depends on Visual Studio. Also,the Windows runners "
"on Github Actions have a too small page-file by default. That needs "
"increasing as the memory consumption is rather high when running the "
